Package Bank

Class NameGenerator

java.lang.Object
NumberManipulation.NumberGenerator
Bank.NameGenerator
public class NameGenerator extends NumberGenerator
This class stores 2,000 (1,000 - boys, 1,000 girls) unique names which can be retrieved only at random. Multiple names are given as an array
